Hey hairdressers !  Your clients hair deserves the best care possible, which is why achieving the perfect lift matters so much. 

By avoiding relying on toners and focusing on a raw blonde with a  flawless lift, we ensure your hair stays vibrant, healthy, and perfectly lifted. Here’s why this approach is tailor-made for you and your clients :

- Experience low-maintenance beauty with a seamless grow-out.
- Attain the ideal lightness without depending on toners.
- Embrace healthier hair with minimized damage.

Trust us to give your hair the attention and care it truly deserves. 

For more education on how to achieve this, please dm !

Love seeing progression! Consistency is key for bright blondes! Want to know how to get this vibrant blonde? 

• coming within 9 weeks for touch ups helps to keep as little dark colors in between as possible 

• embrace warm! Sometimes adding a little gold is what you need to be a platinum blonde

• always use the right shampoos

• staying loyal to one person-  going from salon to salon can cause more chaos and damage

• just have fun! 

 Love you all!!
